quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  3,53,ae perwar-digaar jo ( kitaab ) to ne nazil farmai hai hum is par imaan le aeye aur ( tairay ) paighambar ke muttabe ho chuke to hum ko maan-ne walon mein likh rakh
  3,54,aur woh ( yani yahood qatal eesa ke baray mein aik ) chaal chalay aur khuda bhi ( eesa ko bachanay ke liye ) chaal chala aur khuda khoob chaal chalne wala hai
  3,55,is waqt khuda ne farmaya ke eesa! mein tumhari duniya mein rehne ki muddat poori karkay tum ko apni taraf utha lon ga aur tumhe kafiroon ( ki sohbat ) se pak kar dun ga aur jo log tumhari pairwi karen ge un ko kafiroon par qayamat taq Faiq ( o Ghalib rakhon ga phir tum sab mere paas lout kar aao ge to jin baton mein tum ikhtilaaf karte they is din tum mein un ka faisla kardoon ga
  3,56,yani jo kafir hue un ko duniya aur akhirat ( dono ) mein sakht azaab dun ga aur un ka koi madadgaar nah hoga
  3,57,aur jo imaan laaye aur naik amal karte rahay un ko khuda poora poora sila day ga aur khuda zaalmon ko dost nahi rakhta
  3,58,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) yeh hum tum ko ( khuda ki ) ayatain aur hikmat bhari nsihtin parh parh kar sunaate hain
  3,59,eesa ka haal khuda ke nazdeek aadam ka sa hai ke is ne ( pehlay ) matti se un ka Qalib banaya phir farmaya ke ( ensaan ) ho ja to woh ( ensaan ) ho gay
  3,60,( yeh baat ) tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se haq hai to tum hargiz shak karne walon mein nah hona
  3,61,phir agar yeh log eesa ke baray mein tum se jhagra karen aur tum ko haqeeqat al haal to maloom ho hi chali hai to un se kehna ke aao hum apne biton aur aurton ko bulayen tum apne biton aur aurton ko bulaao aur hum khud bhi ayen aur tum khud bhi aao phir dono fareeq ( khuda se ) duao iltaja ا karen aur jhuton par khuda ki laanat bhejen
